{"tid":409292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍回收場大火 多貓狗死","createTime":"2017-09-22T02:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T05:08:54.000Z","uid":38456,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"72985e70e47032032a692fdcffd4bb2f906636f0","tid":409292,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T02:58:09.000Z","msg":"燒死多貓狗 好心咪咁養<br />\n<br />\n早上8時許，天水圍新錫路新圍一間鐵皮屋起火焚燒，濃煙捲上半空，附近居民紛紛報案求助。據了解，戶主在鐵皮屋收養多頭流浪貓狗，消防接報趕至開喉灌救，約半小時將火救熄，其間救出3籠9隻貓，其中2隻奄奄一息。現場消息稱，場內約有40隻貓狗，其中有20多隻被困慘死。"},{"pid":"745ce5bf9ec7637713ecd4e65b8675b694242e3d","tid":409292,"uid":128271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T03:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f755d8eedfa7c8193daa90c1f020d159b363bbe","tid":409292,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T03:04:53.000Z","msg":"今早經過，好大煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48867d5b7ea8de2f75378c253c5db7463edfe94f","tid":409292,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T03:14:57.000Z","msg":"來生不住天水圍<br />\n<br />\n天水圍個架空指示牌<br />\n天水圍東/濕地公園 個路牌寫埋深圳灣，痴痴地線有無得投訴？"},{"pid":"9ed1256216e41d04226b1f38df433b4b53658944","tid":409292,"uid":10039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T03:17:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f79fdbb7adfaf92bdf3ab46a5cc00e2690ab4f","tid":409292,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T03:48:47.000Z","msg":"天水圍最多支那狗"},{"pid":"e074c406e4aad5b0caa05b189c2aa935c3d4e64e","tid":409292,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi